<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>Killua Zoldyck – Character Details</title>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/styles.css" />
</head>
<body>

  <nav class="navbar">
    <ul class="nav-links">
      <li><a href="index.html">Home</a></li>
      <li><a href="details.html" class="active">Details</a></li>
      <li><a href="about.html">About</a></li>
      <li><a href="new-character-form.html">Add Character</a></li>
    </ul>
  </nav>

  <main class="details-page">

    <div class="details-hero">
      <div class="details-img-wrap">
        <img src="/images/killua.png" alt="Killua Zoldyck" />

        <div class="details-aura killua-aura"></div>
      </div>
      <div class="details-intro">
        <p class="details-eyebrow">Character Profile</p>
        <h1 class="details-name">${character.name}</span></h1>
        <div class="details-tags">
          <span class="tag">Transmutation</span>
          <span class="tag">Assassin</span>
          <span class="tag">Hunter</span>
        </div>
        <p class="details-quote">"I want to be your friend. I said it… your friend."</p>
        <table class="details-table">
          <tbody>
            <tr><th>Universe</th><td>Hunter x Hunter</td></tr>
            <tr><th>Role</th><td>Deuteragonist</td></tr>
            <tr><th>Species</th><td>Human</td></tr>
            <tr><th>Nen Type</th><td>Transmutation</td></tr>
            <tr><th>Age</th><td>12 (pre-timeskip) / 14 (post-timeskip)</td></tr>
            <tr><th>Affiliation</th><td>Zoldyck Family · Hunter Association</td></tr>
            <tr><th>First Appearance</th><td>Chapter 2 / Episode 2 (2011 anime)</td></tr>
            <tr><th>Power Level</th><td>★★★★★</td></tr>
          </tbody>
        </table>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="details-sections">
      <section class="details-block">
        <h2>Backstory</h2>
        <p>Killua Zoldyck was born as the third child of the powerful Zoldyck assassin family, whose compound sits atop Kukuroo Mountain. From infancy he was subjected to brutal conditioning. His days were filled with electric torture, poison exposure, and rigorous combat training. All of this was to sculpt him into the ultimate killing machine. His mother, Kikyo, obsessively controlled his upbringing; his older brother Illumi planted a needle in his brain to enforce obedience and self-preservation at all costs.</p>
        <p>Desperate to escape this destiny, Killua broke free before the Hunter Exam, injuring his own family members to flee. At the Exam he met Gon Freecss, and for the first time in his life experienced something like genuine friendship. This bond becomes the emotional core of the entire series.</p>
      </section>
      <section class="details-block">
        <h2>Abilities &amp; Nen</h2>
        <p>Killua is a Transmuter, able to change the properties of his aura. His signature ability, <strong>Godspeed</strong>, channels electricity through his body to move and react faster than the human eye can track the culmination of years of electric torture that ironically gave him immunity to voltage.</p>
        <ul class="details-list">
          <li><strong>Godspeed </strong> — Lightning-coated speed that exceeds human perception.</li>
          <li><strong>Whirlwind </strong> - Body reacts automatically to danger, bypassing conscious reaction time.</li>
          <li><strong>Lightning Palm </strong> — Focused electric discharge capable of stopping a heart.</li>
          <li><strong>Yo-yo blades</strong> — His preferred weapons before fully mastering Nen, razor-edged and devastating.</li>
        </ul>
      </section>
      <section class="details-block">
        <h2>Personality Traits</h2>
        <p>On the surface Killua is irreverent, sarcastic, and appears effortlessly confident. Beneath that is a deeply wounded child who genuinely believed himself incapable of caring about anyone. His friendship with Gon dismantles this belief piece by piece, though at enormous personal cost.</p>
        <p>His greatest flaw — cowardice engineered by Illumi's needle which haunts him until he physically removes it. After that moment, Killua's loyalty becomes absolute.</p>
      </section>
      <section class="details-block">
        <h2>Key Story Arcs</h2>
        <ul class="details-list">
          <li><strong>Hunter Exam Arc</strong> — Meets Gon; passes but is disqualified for killing a fellow examinee.</li>
          <li><strong>Zoldyck Family Arc</strong> — Gon rescues him from his family's estate; begins real freedom.</li>
          <li><strong>Greed Island Arc</strong> — Trains extensively; unlocks Nen potential.</li>
          <li><strong>Chimera Ant Arc</strong> — Achieves Godspeed to protect Gon; confronts Illumi's psychological conditioning.</li>
          <li><strong>13th Hunter Chairman Election Arc</strong> — Removes Illumi's needle; departs to care for Alluka/Nanika.</li>
        </ul>
      </section>
    </div>

  <div class="details-back">
    <a href="index.html" class="btn-back">&larr; Back to Gallery</a>
    <a href="about.html" class="btn-back">About This Site</a>
    <a href="new-character-form.html" class="btn-back">Add a Character</a>
  </div>

  </main>

</body>
</html>